SAFEGUARDS AND FAILURE MODES

Red Team Analysis: What Could Go Wrong?

Scenario 1: Elite Capture Attempt

· Risk: Powerful groups try to control AI-ADN
· Mitigation: Distributed consensus requires 80% of leaf nodes
· Backup: Code fragmentation across 1B+ devices prevents takeover

Scenario 2: Mass Unemployment Shock

· Risk: Rapid automation displaces workers
· Mitigation: UAR scales with automation gains
· Transition: 20-year retraining program with wage support

Scenario 3: Geopolitical Resistance

· Risk: Nations ban fractal systems
· Mitigation: Borderless nature of mesh networks
· Diplomacy: Demonstrate benefits to ruling elites

Scenario 4: Technological Failure

· Risk: Critical bug in AI-ADN
· Mitigation: Multiple redundant validation layers
· Recovery: 24-hour rollback capability to last stable state

